##Public vs Private
Know the difference between AWS Public and AWS Private - focuses on the networking aspect

## CloudFormation Basics

Tool that lets you create, update, delete reources through a template in AWS. 
Templates written in YAML or JSON

YAML: 
-Easier to make mistakes with

-All templates have a list of "resorces"
-The resouces section of a template is the only mandatory section of a template
-Description: free text section; only restriction is that if you have both description and a template format version - if you use both, the description *must* follow the "templateformatversion". ..



